# 📊 Vrinda Store Sales Dashboard (Excel)

## 📌 Objective
Analyze 2022 sales data using Excel to understand customer trends and improve business decisions.

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Charts
- Slicers

---

## 📊 Dashboard Features
- Sales vs Orders comparison
- Gender-based analysis
- Order status breakdown
- Top states analysis
- Channel contribution
- Category performance

---

## 📈 Key Insights
- Women contribute around 65% of sales
- Amazon is the top sales channel
- Maharashtra is the top-performing state
- March has the highest sales
- Most orders are successfully delivered

